Arthur Lucan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Lucan 0 Arthur Lucan (16 September 1885 – 17 May 1954) was an English actor who performed the drag act Old Mother Riley on stage, radio and screen, with a series of comedy films from the late 1930s to the early 1950s.
